name: Serie Tribute: 10 - Morgan Le Fay
description:
This new series has a collectible card format. It will make a tribute tour about superheroes and villains. A new creative venture of Roboto Inc. for its great collectors. Prototypes designed by Norma Xelda Jara. Let's have fun! 

Also known as Morgana, Morgaine and Vivian Morgan, Le Fay is an incredibly magical person. She wears that green dress with the deep V, has a belt of skulls like Mystique. Her big enemies are usually Merlin, King Arthur and the Dark Knight, as well as Scarlet Witch, Spider-Woman and Iron Man. 
First appearance: The Demon Vol. 1 #1 (September 1972)
